VISION:

An API to keep track of elected officials and their associated Twitter accounts.

Right now, I aim to take advantage of Twitter lists. And, to be able to programatically scrape info about members of any given public body and 
then attempt to find their Twitter accounts.

https://trello.com/b/EwqKcBIg/governors-project
^Trello link for coordinated work. Please, fork this repo and help me build this.


//--------------------------

for: People interested in politics, public announcements, or government/democracy 

who: want to connect directly with members of their government

the: list aggregator 
is a: crawler/scraper
unlike:  
our solution: to gather data from good sources as much as possible and verify it through different strategies to get accurate 
information.
